{"tid":342450,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"［dunkirk]連登冇人睇編寫美好時光？","createTime":"2017-07-31T15:16:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-03T19:10:00.000Z","uid":88117,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f7b2d1f6760b511d88aca74db372a2ee3e16c6e1","tid":342450,"uid":88117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T15:16:16.000Z","msg":"同樣都係用dunkirk做背景，但完全係令一個故事，一幕打鬥都冇。<br />\n<br />\n今日睇左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 雖然冇話好感動，但睇完好舒服，好治癒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 原全冇平時戰爭片果種沉重，個呀叔好好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 啲配樂都好正<br />\n<br />\n建議大家睇完dunkirk再去睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9b1ee808cfab6472892c48e269830cdc16e516f","tid":342450,"uid":4260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T15:25:10.000Z","msg":"bill nighy同個美軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce02f3394e6e8820b8d8a73a5a1919c0ae2f3080","tid":342450,"uid":71358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T15:29:06.000Z","msg":"個ending好sad....人生無常就係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff8273057329f8c1144090091455a66a531015ad","tid":342450,"uid":14070,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T15:33:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個ending好sad....人生無常就係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我覺得死得好突兀"},{"pid":"9e08f96ccb5e4a067c1851fe68208adb7281822d","tid":342450,"uid":14070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T15:33:38.000Z","msg":"睇完dunkirk 第二日就睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7b5a39427c21b315c3c0c52e49dfcc6b46df7df","tid":342450,"uid":48479,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T15: